casebody.data:
Backus et al., Respondents, v. Yandell, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and Country, General Term. January 16, 1890.) Appeal from trial term.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Bischoff, J.

F. M. Littlefield, for appellant. W. S. Beaman, for respondents.

No opinion. Ordered that the judgment be affirmed, with costs.
